{"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"API Collection","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"title":"Remote Desktop Access","role":"collectionGroup"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Connect to Spooktacular VMs via VNC for remote development, QA testing, and design review."}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/EC2MacDeployment","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KubernetesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/CLIReference"],"title":"Related Guides","anchor":"Related-Guides"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/VirtualMachineSpecification","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/VirtualMachineConfiguration","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/NetworkMode","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/RemoteDesktopTemplate"],"title":"Key Types","anchor":"Key-Types"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/CLIReference","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GitHubActionsGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/JenkinsGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/EC2MacDeployment","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KubernetesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/MLWorkloads","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/OpenClawGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/BlueBubblesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Versioning"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Guides","title":"Guides"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Spooktacular VMs include full macOS display output backed by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"virtual GPU (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"VZMacGraphicsDeviceConfiguration"},{"text":"). Combined with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"macOS’s built-in Screen Sharing (VNC) server, this enables remote","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"graphical access to any VM from anywhere on your network.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Use-Cases","text":"Use Cases"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Remote development"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — Full macOS desktop for Xcode, Interface","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Builder, and Simulator from any machine","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"QA testing"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — Manual testing of macOS and iOS apps in a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"controlled, reproducible VM environment","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Design review"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — Share a running app with designers and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"stakeholders without giving them SSH access","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Training and demos"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — Provide ephemeral macOS desktops for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"workshops or customer demos","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Help desk"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — Remote access to user-like macOS environments","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for support and troubleshooting","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Enabling-Screen-Sharing-via-Provisioning","text":"Enabling Screen Sharing via Provisioning"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The most reliable way to enable VNC access is through a provisioning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"script that runs automatically when the VM boots.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Using-disk-inject-Zero-Touch","text":"Using disk-inject (Zero-Touch)"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["spook create desktop-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --cpu 4 --memory 8 --disk 64 \\","    --displays 1 \\","    --user-data ~\/enable-screensharing.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Where ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"enable-screensharing.sh"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"bash","code":["#!\/bin\/bash","set -euo pipefail","","# Enable Screen Sharing (VNC server)","sudo launchctl load -w \/System\/Library\/LaunchDaemons\/com.apple.screensharing.plist","","# Set the VNC password (for VNC-only clients)","sudo defaults write \/Library\/Preferences\/com.apple.RemoteManagement VNCAlwaysStartOnConsole -bool true","","# Enable Remote Management for full control","sudo \/System\/Library\/CoreServices\/RemoteManagement\/ARDAgent.app\/Contents\/Resources\/kickstart \\","    -activate \\","    -configure -access -on \\","    -configure -allowAccessFor -allUsers \\","    -configure -restart -agent -privs -all","","echo \"Screen Sharing enabled\""],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Using-the-Kubernetes-CRD","text":"Using the Kubernetes CRD"},{"syntax":"yaml","code":["apiVersion: spooktacular.io\/v1alpha1","kind: MacOSVM","metadata:","  name: remote-desktop","  namespace: desktops","spec:","  image: ghcr.io\/spooktacular\/macos:15.4","  resources:","    cpu: 4","    memory: 8Gi","    disk: 64Gi","  displays: 1","  network:","    mode: bridged","    interface: en0","  provisioning:","    mode: disk-inject","    userData: |","      #!\/bin\/bash","      sudo launchctl load -w \/System\/Library\/LaunchDaemons\/com.apple.screensharing.plist","      sudo \/System\/Library\/CoreServices\/RemoteManagement\/ARDAgent.app\/Contents\/Resources\/kickstart \\","          -activate -configure -access -on \\","          -configure -allowAccessFor -allUsers \\","          -configure -restart -agent -privs -all"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"See ","type":"text"},{"text":"doc:Provisioning","type":"text"},{"text":" for details on all four ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"strategies.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Connecting-via-VNC","text":"Connecting via VNC"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"macOS-Screen-Sharing-App-Built-in","text":"macOS Screen Sharing App (Built-in)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The simplest way to connect from another Mac:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Find the VM’s IP address:","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["spook ip desktop-vm","# 192.168.64.3"],"type":"codeListing"},{"start":2,"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Open Screen Sharing (Cmd+K in Finder, or open the Screen Sharing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"app directly):","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["open vnc:\/\/192.168.64.3"],"type":"codeListing"},{"start":3,"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Authenticate with the guest macOS user credentials.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anch